    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-moss-deep">Why MoodSupplement exists</h1>
    <div class="prose-mr mt-6">
      <p>MoodSupplement started from a simple frustration: most pages selling mood supplements either over-promise wildly or bury the cautions that actually matter. We wanted a place that treats readers like adults — clear about what the research shows, honest about what it doesn't, and never pretending a capsule can replace real care.</p>

